  ('optician-moex-01432', 'optician', 'optician-moex-109-72ff33b8', 'sub-optician-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '為了不造成眼睛刺激不適，隱形眼鏡護理液（如沖洗劑、消毒劑等）的滲透壓（osmolality）須維持在：', '["3～3.5mOsmol/kg", "30～35mOsmol/kg", "300～350mOsmol/kg", "3000～3500mOsmol/kg"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:33+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ae4233b96821", "answer_pdf_sha1": "fc9bd5d8075c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109110", "c": "113", "s": "1108", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學概要", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、109年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
